<Base title="APFS-RS Quality Gates">
  <h1>Quality Gates</h1>
  <p>Local/CI Rust gates require format, clippy, nextest, 90% coverage, fuzz smoke, mutation testing, property testing, and supply-chain checks.</p>
  <pre><code>cargo nextest run --workspace --all-features
cargo llvm-cov nextest --workspace --all-features --fail-under-lines 90
cargo mutants --workspace</code></pre>
</Base>
